<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8"?>
<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>19103</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“哦，天啊。”悟空想，“黄眉大王来了！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>19104</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>24445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空跳起来，飞快地从寺院里跑了出去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>24446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>28734</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑到外面时，大家都在等着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>28735</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>31737</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“行李呢？”悟净问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>31738</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>35180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空看了看自己空着的手。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>35181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>39608</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他打了一下额头。“行李好像掉了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>39609</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>43343</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空听见寺院里传来脚步声。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>43344</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>47851</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在不是担心行李的时候。”悟空小声说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>47852</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>53353</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黄眉大王来了。我们得走，快！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>53354</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>62852</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他帮唐僧骑上马。他们赶紧上了路。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>62853</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>70225</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“快跑，八戒！”悟净生气地低声说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>70226</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>79352</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒气喘吁吁地说：“我......不......喜欢......跑！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>79353</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>85605</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他们没跑多远，黄眉大王就飞到了他们上面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>85606</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>89922</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们逃不掉的！”妖怪大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>89923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>93807</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“还有，你们去不了西天。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>93808</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>99420</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我是真正的佛教徒。我会拿到真经的！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>99421</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>104421</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空、八戒，还有悟净，都拿出了兵器。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>104422</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>亢金龙露出了爪子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>116419</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄眉大王嘲笑说：“你们真的以为能打得过我？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>116420</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>120417</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他从袍子里拿出了那块布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>120418</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>124668</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>八戒放下钉耙笑了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>124669</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>129918</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们有很厉害的兵器，而你只有一块布！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>129919</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>134172</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那不是普通的布。”亢金龙提醒道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>134173</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>139711</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄眉大王把布扔向他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>139712</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>143318</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心！”悟空大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>143319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149065</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空在那块布要包住其他人时，飞到了空中。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149066</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>151902</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪马上捡起了布。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>151903</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>156000</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他跑回寺院，摔上了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>156001</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>159601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空坐在云上思考。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>159602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>163428</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他怎么才能救出其他人呢？</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>163429</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165479</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“不能求玉帝帮忙。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165480</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>169817</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他已经派了亢金龙，可亢金龙刚才又被抓住了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>169818</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>172952</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>可以求观音菩萨帮忙。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>172953</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>178453</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空正在想该怎么办，有两个神仙来了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>35</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>178454</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182528</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>一个是乌龟，一个是大蛇。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>36</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182529</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>186791</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>两个神仙各拿着剑和盾。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>37</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>186792</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192619</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们来自武当山。”乌龟说，“是来帮你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>38</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192620</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>195558</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>大蛇点了点头。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>39</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>195559</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>200445</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“听说唐僧被叫黄眉大王的妖怪抓住了。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>40</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>200446</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>204018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“谢谢你们来。”悟空说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>41</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>204019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>208521</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他马上把发生的事情告诉了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>42</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>208522</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>212019</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“现在去寺院吧。”乌龟说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>43</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>212020</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>215780</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黄眉大王打不过我们三个的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>44</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>215781</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>217840</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我们太厉害了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>45</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>217841</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>222052</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他不是我们的对手。”大蛇补充道。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>46</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>222053</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>228303</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空带着两个神仙去了寺院。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>47</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>228304</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>233309</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你们要小心那妖怪的一块布。”悟空提醒道，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>48</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>233310</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>236168</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他会用那个抓我们的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>49</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>236169</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>239568</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空敲了敲寺院的门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>50</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>239569</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>243338</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“黄眉大王！马上放了唐僧他们！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>51</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>243339</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>246518</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>否则，我推倒你的寺院！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>52</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>246519</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>250018</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>然后，再毁了你整座山！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>53</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>250019</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>252520</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>门突然打开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>54</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>252521</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>257180</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>黄眉大王出来，把那块布扔了过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>55</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>257181</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>263220</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“小心！”悟空大喊。悟空跳起躲开了。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>56</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>263221</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>268601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>乌龟和大蛇不够快。布包住了他们。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>57</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>268602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>274972</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>妖怪笑着捡起布又回到寺院里。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>58</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>274973</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>277968</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空又飞到天上。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>59</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>277969</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>284690</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他坐在云上嘟囔道：“现在我该怎么办呢？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>60</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>284691</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>289771</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>这时，一个声音传来：“你好！悟空！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>61</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>289772</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>293601</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空朝声音传来的方向看过去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>62</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>293602</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>298068</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>是一个大肚子男人。男人微笑着。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>63</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>298069</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>301713</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你知道我是谁吗？”那男人问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>64</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>301714</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>306058</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>悟空笑着说：“您是弥勒佛。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>65</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>306059</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>313037</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对。”弥勒佛说，“我是来帮你的。”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
</Subtitle>